<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<div class="row justify-content-center my-5">
  <div class="col-lg-8">
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg rounded-4 p-5 bg-white">
      <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-contract text-danger me-2"></i>Terms of Service
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted small">Last Updated: May 23, 2026</p>
      <hr class="my-4">
      
      <div class="text-secondary" style="line-height: 1.7;">
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark">1. Acceptance of Terms</h5>
        <p>By accessing or using the WonderFull hotel booking application, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please refrain from using the platform.</p>
        
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mt-4">2. Host and Guest Regulations</h5>
        <p>Hosts are responsible for listing accurate, clean, and available accommodations. Guests must abide by house rules, check-in schedules, and treat properties with care. Standard cancellation and refund policies apply based on check-in proximity.</p>
        
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mt-4">3. Payments and Cancellation</h5>
        <p>Bookings are secured via Razorpay or verified UPI UTR codes. Cancellations follow the tier-based refund system (10% fee if >72 hours, 25% fee if 24h-72h, 50% fee if <24 hours, and 100% deduction after check-in has passed).</p>
        
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mt-4">4. Limitation of Liability</h5>
        <p>WonderFull acts as an intermediary connecting guests with hosts. We are not liable for listing inaccuracies, property disputes, or financial transaction gateway failures.</p>
        
        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mt-4">5. Modifications to Service</h5>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or terminate the services offered on WonderFull at any time without prior notice.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-top text-center">
        <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-danger rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold shadow-sm">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-1"></i>Back to Explore
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
